    DS "No volveré a ser tan indulgente."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1082
translate spanish d1a_warn_a944719d:

    # As "Mh..."
    As "Mh..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1086
translate spanish d1a_warn_e5ac6020:

    # DS "That's mine."
    DS "Eso es mío."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1090
translate spanish d1a_toss_0e57fc9a:

    # DS "I'm done with you."
    DS "Ya he terminado contigo."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1094
translate spanish d1a_toss_fcd697d3:

    # DS "Now get out of my sight."
    DS "Ahora sal de mi vista."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1098
translate spanish d1a_toss_e5ac6020:

    # DS "That's mine."
    DS "Eso es mío."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1101
translate spanish d1a_toss_8b33480a:

    # DS "If I see you again, I'll probably kill you."
    DS "Si te vuelvo a ver, probablemente te mate."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1104
translate spanish d1a_toss_ec7695b5:

    # As "Hn..."
    As "Hn..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1112
translate spanish d1a8_97f0c146:

    # "Finally..."
    "Por fin..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1115
translate spanish d1a8_030a926a:

    # DSt "I'm getting too old for this shit."
    DSt "Me estoy haciendo demasiado viejo para esta mierda."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1116
translate spanish d1a8_1c4de80c:

    # DSt "Next time I may not be as lucky..."
    DSt "La próxima vez puede que no tenga tanta suerte..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1125
translate spanish d1b_342999f5:

    # "{i}*Driving off*{/i}"
    "{i}*El se aleja conduciendo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1126
translate spanish d1b_ffc47d9f:

    # "Several hours later"
    "Varias horas después"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1127
translate spanish d1b_dc4b2253:

    # DS "{i}I wish I could have seen it when the place was still, as it was meant to be..{/i}"
    DS "{i}Ojalá hubiera podido verlo cuando el lugar aún estaba como debía estar...{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1132
translate spanish d1b_e0865d59:

    # DS "{i}But that was before my time.{/i}"
    DS "{i}Pero eso fue antes de mi tiempo.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1133
translate spanish d1b_e704b282:

    # DS "{i}All I have, all that remains, are ruins and the stories about the great war.{/i}"
    DS "{i}Todo lo que tengo, todo lo que queda, son ruinas y las historias sobre la gran guerra.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1134
translate spanish d1b_3e48dcb3:

    # DS "{i}And even those are mostly gone. All that survives is the memory of the final assault, of the End of Days.{/i}"
    DS "{i}Y aun esos casi han desaparecido. Todo lo que queda es el recuerdo del asalto final, del Fin de los Días.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1135
translate spanish d1b_1c6e4fa0:

    # DS "{i}The eternal flames burned into a sky forever marked, a living, shifting memory of the flames of the past...{/i}"
    DS "{i}Las llamas eternas arden en un cielo marcado para siempre, un recuerdo vivo y cambiante de las llamas del pasado...{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1136
translate spanish d1b_52b86b6b:

    # DS "{i}... the ultimate finger pointed at our folly, by the world itself, to admonish us, perhaps, about the cost of our hubris.{/i}"
    DS "{i}... El dedo definitivo apuntando a nuestra locura, por parte del mundo mismo, para advertirnos, quizás, sobre el costo de nuestra arrogancia.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1139
translate spanish d1b_d258e781:

    # DS "{i}Decades turned into centuries, and despite everything, like cockroaches, we endured.{/i}"
    DS "{i}Décadas se convirtieron en siglos, y a pesar de todo, como cucarachas, sobrevivimos.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1140
translate spanish d1b_62f186c7:

    # DS "{i}And after all those years, somewhere along the path of history; me.{/i}"
    DS "{i}Y después de todos esos años, en algún lugar a lo largo del camino de la historia; yo.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1144
translate spanish d1b_4fd72cfe:

    # Zt "My name is [persistent.player_name], and I am what they call a Desert Stalker. Trained in the city of Zeta and commissioned by Queen Merneith."
    Zt "Mi nombre es [persistent.player_name], Acechador del Desierto. Entrenado en la ciudad de Zeta y comisionado por la Reina Merneith."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1145
translate spanish d1b_c1ad90a3:

    # Zt "My task, today, is to hunt for ancient artifacts left undiscovered..."
    Zt "Mi tarea, hoy, es buscar artefactos antiguos que no se hayan descubierto..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1146
translate spanish d1b_af6927c9:

    # Zt "Officially, with the purpose of helping restore our civilisation."
    Zt "Oficialmente, con el propósito de ayudar a restaurar nuestra civilización."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1147
translate spanish d1b_43a0e15a:

    # Zt "...But all the silly statuette is good for is making Zeta, her domain, look pretty."
    Zt "... pero todo lo que sirve esa ridícula estatuilla es para hacer que Zeta, su dominio, se vea bonito."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1148
translate spanish d1b_a216ad33:

    # Zt "Unlike the pile of rubble that is testing my suspensions right now. Jewel of the Nile it would be, except the river too is but a distant memory."
    Zt "A diferencia de los escombros que están poniendo a prueba mis suspensiones ahora mismo. Joya del Nilo sería, excepto que el río también es solo un recuerdo distante."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1149
translate spanish d1b_db2e3a32:

    # Zt "I can't blame the Queen, though. She rules over what is effectively the only place that can be called a city in the entire region."
    Zt "No puedo culpar a la Reina, sin embargo. Gobierna lo que es efectivamente el único lugar que puede llamarse ciudad en toda la región."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1150
translate spanish d1b_58755dfe:

    # Zt "It's the only large city in the region..."
    Zt "Es la única ciudad grande de la región..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1151
translate spanish d1b_46da2187:

    # Zt "Possibly the only place left where there are rules in place for the strong as well as the weak."
    Zt "Posiblemente el único lugar que queda donde hay reglas tanto para los fuertes como para los débiles."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1152
translate spanish d1b_69473f89:

    # Zt "Sparse rules, to be sure, but they are there."
    Zt "Reglas escasas, sin duda, pero están ahí."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1155
translate spanish d1b_3a73cdef:

    # Zt "Yes, things are not always fair, and the strong are favoured over the weak..."
    Zt "Sí, las cosas no siempre son justas, y los fuertes tienen ventaja sobre los débiles..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1156
translate spanish d1b_fd0e2c4e:

    # Zt "...but that's nothing compared to the world out here."
    Zt "... pero eso no es nada comparado con el mundo de allá afuera."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1157
translate spanish d1b_0439da78:

    # Zt "I can count myself lucky. Not all Stalkers have access to the Palace the way I do, with opportunity to get the better paid commissions..."
    Zt "Me considero afortunado. No todos los Stalkers tienen acceso al Palacio como yo, con la oportunidad de conseguir las comisiones mejor pagadas..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1158
translate spanish d1b_59393443:

    # Zt "Even so, I have to follow my own path and am forever on the road, scouring the desert so I can provide for my family."
    Zt "Aun así, debo seguir mi propio camino y estoy siempre en la carretera, explorando el desierto para poder mantener a mi familia."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1159
translate spanish d1b_f1b8b9ca:

    # Zt "It would be nice if the city hadn't banned ancient technology outright."
    Zt "Sería agradable si la ciudad no hubiera prohibido la tecnología antigua por completo."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1160
translate spanish d1b_72194cb0:

    # Zt "Instead, I have to make a whole detour for something as simple as getting fuel for my car..."
    Zt "En cambio, tengo que dar un rodeo completo por algo tan simple como conseguir combustible para mi coche..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1164
translate spanish d1b_d5790bd9:

    # Zt "Anyway, here we are."
    Zt "De todos modos, aquí estamos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1165
translate spanish d1b_a0bdd97a:

    # Zt "The outskirts of Old Cairo."
    Zt "Las afueras del Viejo Cairo."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1166
translate spanish d1b_fd2f9e75:

    # Zt "An example of what the rest of the world might look like..."
    Zt "Un ejemplo de cómo podría lucir el resto del mundo..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1167
translate spanish d1b_adff740e:

    # Zt "This godforsaken place is no place to live. But humans always find a way."
    Zt "Este lugar maldito no es un lugar para vivir. Pero los humanos siempre encuentran una manera."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1168
translate spanish d1b_7d435976:

    # Zt "...Or what is left of them."
    Zt "... o lo que queda de ellos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1169
translate spanish d1b_a372a009:

    # Zt "No one knows if it is the pollution or the burned air..."
    Zt "Nadie sabe si es la contaminación o el aire quemado..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1170
translate spanish d1b_6fb2017a:

    # Zt "...Or a combination of both."
    Zt "... ¿o una combinación de ambos?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1171
translate spanish d1b_c2328b40:

    # Zt "But the people here are different. It's like they turned into living mummies."
    Zt "Pero la gente aquí es diferente. Es como si se hubieran convertido en momias vivientes."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1172
translate spanish d1b_723ff885:

    # Zt "That is why they call themselves the Decayed."
    Zt "Por eso se llaman los Decaídos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1173
translate spanish d1b_b00e3459:

    # Zt "Their untamed will to cling on to whatever little they have made most of them rot from the inside out, in this place that isn't meant for the living."
    Zt "Su voluntad indomable de aferrarse a lo poco que tienen ha hecho que la mayoría de ellos se pudran por dentro en este lugar que no está hecho para los vivos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1174
translate spanish d1b_9168f660:

    # Zt "But I know some of this place and its people. And I am known to them."
    Zt "Pero conozco algo de este lugar y su gente. Y soy conocido por ellos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1175
translate spanish d1b_06b7fc7f:

    # Zt "Since no one at home knows or cares to know how to process fuel, these people come in quite handy, crafty as they are."
    Zt "Dado que nadie en casa sabe o se preocupa por saber cómo procesar combustible, esta gente es bastante útil, ingeniosa como es."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1176
translate spanish d1b_97f06972:

    # Zt "It's nothing but rumors, but it's said the decayed have slaves working at an old oil refinery somewhere in the north."
    Zt "No es más que un rumor, pero dicen que los Decayed tienen esclavos trabajando en una vieja refinería de petróleo en algún lugar del norte."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1177
translate spanish d1b_a49178eb:

    # Zt "Time to remind them of our agreement and get some of that fuel."
    Zt "Es hora de recordarles nuestro acuerdo y conseguir algo de ese combustible."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1178
translate spanish d1b_9863897a:

    # Zt "But first I have to find them."
    Zt "Pero primero tengo que encontrarlos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1179
translate spanish d1b_ca558cd7:

    # Zt "It should be right down the road, but I also hear noises from the ruins."
    Zt "Debería estar al final de la carretera, pero también oigo ruidos procedentes de las ruinas."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1180
translate spanish d1b_80dfd09d:

    # Zt "Not sure if I should investigate it..."
    Zt "No estoy seguro de si debería investigarlo..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1200
translate spanish choice3_city_38773a40:

    # Zt "Let's follow the road and see where it leads me."
    Zt "Sigamos el camino y veamos a dónde me lleva."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1203
translate spanish choice3_city_e5fa83a9:

    # Z "Now I remember... there, the building on the right."
    Z "Ahora recuerdo... Allí, el edificio de la derecha."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1206
translate spanish choice3_city_e1e02c71:

    # Z "The warehouse is always closed..."
    Z "El almacén está siempre cerrado..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1209
translate spanish choice3_city_3774cdae:

    # Zt "This must be it."
    Zt "Esto debe ser."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1210
translate spanish choice3_city_1e53b3da:

    # Z "Shaqiq... Remember our agreement... the black wall."
    Z "Shaqiq... Recuerda nuestro acuerdo... El muro negro."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1211
translate spanish choice3_city_a33f9957:

    # C "[persistent.player_name!c]? Yes yes... we remember..."
    C "¿[persistent.player_name!c]? Sí, sí... Nos acordamos..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1212
translate spanish choice3_city_bdbb8997:

    # C "You filled your tank just a week ago, it's a bit too soo-"
    C "Has llenado el depósito hace apenas una semana, es un poco demasiado así que..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1213
translate spanish choice3_city_c95a8478:

    # Z "This is not a discussion."
    Z "Esto no se trata de un debate."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1214
translate spanish choice3_city_94f41df3:

    # Z "If you don't keep your end of the bargain, our deal is history."
    Z "Si no cumplís vuestra parte del trato, nuestro trato será historia."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1215
translate spanish choice3_city_a0e683cd:

    # Z "And God have mercy on your pitiful souls if that ever happens."
    Z "Y que Dios se apiade de vuestras lamentables almas si eso llega a ocurrir."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1216
translate spanish choice3_city_115b8577:

    # C "Master [persistent.player_name], there is no need to threaten us. We know."
    C "Amo [persistent.player_name], no es necesario que nos amenaces. Lo sabemos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1217
translate spanish choice3_city_63ed9329:

    # C "Give me just a moment..."
    C "Dame un momento..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1220
translate spanish choice3_city_81deb29d:

    # C "Here... this is all we can spare at the moment..."
    C "Toma... esto es todo lo que podemos disponer en este momento..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1221
translate spanish choice3_city_6d36c534:

    # C "It's hard to come by the..."
    C "Es difícil encontrar el..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1222
translate spanish choice3_city_158fb52d:

    # Z "Spare me your excuses. But this will do for now."
    Z "Ahórrate tus excusas. Pero esto servirá por ahora."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1225
translate spanish choice3_city_06d2f3fe:

    # "{i}You take the fuel can and ready yourself to leave."
    "{i}Tomas el bidón de combustible y te preparas para salir."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1228
translate spanish choice3_city_12e0b656:

    # C "Goodbye [persistent.player_name], and drive carefully..."
    C "Adiós [persistent.player_name], y conduce con cuidado..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1229
translate spanish choice3_city_446042fc:

    # C "You don't want to drop into one of the feeding pits, trust me."
    C "No querrás caer en uno de los pozos de infección, créeme."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1230
translate spanish choice3_city_d10f4294:

    # "{i}Inaudible chatting and laughing"
    "{i}Charla inaudible y risas"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1231
translate spanish choice3_city_3e7f1f32:

    # Zt "Creepy bastard."
    Zt "Maldito bastardo."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1234
translate spanish choice3_city_f0e0f53a:

    # "You walk back to the car..."
    "Vuelves al coche..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1242
translate spanish choice3_city_91905fa7:

    # Zt " I should take a look..."
    Zt "Debería echar un vistazo..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1245
translate spanish choice3_city_0c73d22c:

    # C2 "{i}*inaudible chatter*"
    C2 "{i}*charla inaudible*"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1246
translate spanish choice3_city_4aa71cc0:

    # C2 "Hahaha, I told you I was right, didn't I?"
    C2 "Jajaja, te dije que tenía razón, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1247
translate spanish choice3_city_7f820454:

    # C3 "...Do you know why they look like this?"
    C3 "... ¿Sabes por qué tienen este aspecto?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1248
translate spanish choice3_city_d7c5a4f1:

    # C2 "I have no idea, and I don't really care."
    C2 "No tengo idea, y realmente no me importa."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1249
translate spanish choice3_city_731fe538:

    # C3 "She looks... unsettling. Now that I see one up close, I am not surprised they are hunted like animals."
    C3 "Parece... inquietante. Ahora que veo uno de cerca, no me sorprende que los cacen como animales."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1250
translate spanish choice3_city_42dc4926:

    # C2 "Who says they aren't? Some say we are animals too. Outside of Cairo we're hunted too, did you forget?"
    C2 "¿Quién dice que no lo son? Algunos dicen que nosotros también somos animales. Fuera del Viejo Cairo también nos cazan, ¿lo olvidaste?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1253
translate spanish choice3_city_c3eaf98c:

    # C2 "Ah look who we have here. Our old friend [persistent.player_name]."
    C2 "Ah mira a quien tenemos aquí. Nuestro viejo amigo [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1254
translate spanish choice3_city_d70eeb74:

    # Z "[Ki], what is going on here?"
    Z "[Ki], ¿qué está pasando aquí?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1255
translate spanish choice3_city_04ed1beb:

    # Ki "Brother [Ko] is showing me the elf he caught a few days ago."
    Ki "El hermano [Ko] me está mostrando la elfa que atrapó hace unos días."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1258
translate spanish choice3_city_f4d3d7a9:

    # Ko "Yes, come look. She's... well, see for yourself."
    Ko "Sí, ven a mirar. Ella... bueno, mira por ti mismo."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1259
translate spanish choice3_city_060f731a:

    # Ko "Come, come..."
    Ko "Ven, ven..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1262
translate spanish choice3_city_ea9abec7:

    # Ko "See? Not a scratch on her, because I caught her half asleep."
    Ko "¿Ves? Ni un rasguño en ella, porque la atrapé medio dormida."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1263
translate spanish choice3_city_1b7e065a:

    # C2 "And look at her skin, so soft."
    C2 "Y mira su piel, tan suave."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1264
translate spanish choice3_city_8d472087:

    # Z "She is starving."
    Z "Ella está hambrienta."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1267
translate spanish choice3_city_8ed826e9:

    # Ko "I know, who cares?"
    Ko "Lo sé, ¿a quién le importa?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1268
translate spanish choice3_city_748e2cf6:

    # Ko "Everyone here is hungry. Some get to eat; others, like her, get eaten."
    Ko "Todos aquí tienen hambre. Algunos comen; otros, como ella, son comida."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1271
translate spanish choice3_city_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1275
translate spanish scene4_ivy_301c062d:

    # Z "What is that thing around her neck?"
    Z "¿Qué es esa cosa que lleva en el cuello?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1278
translate spanish scene4_ivy_8e97bc94:

    # Ko "Oh that..."
    Ko "¡Oh, eso...!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1279
translate spanish scene4_ivy_a7b8db2b:

    # Ko "It looks like a collar, right? But it's not a normal collar!"
    Ko "Parece un collar, ¿verdad? Pero no es un collar normal."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1280
translate spanish scene4_ivy_fb3c1372:

    # Ko "It's equipped with a sensor that goes off if the wearer moves too far away from the keys [Ki] is holding."
    Ko "Está equipado con un sensor que se activa si el portador se aleja demasiado de las llaves que sostiene [Ki]."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1283
translate spanish scene4_ivy_6c3a379e:

    # Ki "Come dinner time, you'll see how it works."
    Ki "A la hora de la cena, verás cómo funciona."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1289
translate spanish scene4_ivy_253940ac:

    # Z "What were you talking about just now when you mentioned her looks?"
    Z "¿De qué estabais hablando hace un momento cuando habéis mencionado su aspecto?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1290
translate spanish scene4_ivy_0c1d5020:

    # Ko "Her ears! What else?"
    Ko "¡Sus orejas! ¿Qué más?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1291
translate spanish scene4_ivy_b2271d8a:

    # Ko "They're the whole reason why people call them elves, like a creature from a fairytale!"
    Ko "Ellos son la razón por la que la gente los llama elfos, como criaturas de un cuento de hadas."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1292
translate spanish scene4_ivy_000e28fe:

    # Ko "Yet here she is, in the flesh."
    Ko "Y aquí está ella, en carne y hueso."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1307
translate spanish scene4_ivy_0d3b023a:

    # Z "What are you going to do to her now?"
    Z "¿Qué la vas a hacer ahora?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1308
translate spanish scene4_ivy_961c4960:

    # Ko "Mhhh I think we'll stick to what I planned for her."
    Ko "Mhhh. Creo que nos ceñiremos a lo que he planeado para ella."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1309
translate spanish scene4_ivy_c22284b4:

    # Ki "[Ko] is right."
    Ki "[Ko] tiene razón."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1310
translate spanish scene4_ivy_175fbc82:

    # Ko "Unless you want her for yourself, Stalker. Hrhrhr."
    Ko "A menos que la quieras para ti, Acechador. Jejeje."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1311
translate spanish scene4_ivy_51d91a91:

    # Ki "Wait, you're not giving her away just like that are you?"
    Ki "Espera, no se la estarás entregando así como así ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1312
translate spanish scene4_ivy_2ef1f934:

    # Ko "Of course not [Ki], I'm not stupid..."
    Ko "Claro que no [Ki], no soy estúpido..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1313
translate spanish scene4_ivy_4a057974:

    # Ko "Listen Stalker, you know how it works in Old Cairo..."
    Ko "Escucha Acechador, ya sabes cómo funciona el Viejo Cairo..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1314
translate spanish scene4_ivy_544c69d7:

    # Ko "...and I know why you're here."
    Ko "... y sé por qué estás aquí."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1315
translate spanish scene4_ivy_9f7321fb:

    # Ko "You are after our fuel supplies, which means you've been somewhere far enough that whatever you found there must have been worth it."
    Ko "Vas detrás de nuestras reservas de combustible, lo que significa que has estado en algún lugar lo suficientemente lejano como para que lo que encontraste allí haya valido la pena."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1316
translate spanish scene4_ivy_69d3f124:

    # Ko "I'll make you an offer..."
    Ko "Te haré una oferta..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1317
translate spanish scene4_ivy_771e081c:

    # Ko "You hand over whatever precious item you found, and I'll hand over this very fine specimen to you."
    Ko "Entregas cualquier objeto valioso que encontraste, y yo te entregaré este espécimen tan fino."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1318
translate spanish scene4_ivy_4814ca39:

    # Ko "She will be yours, along with the collar and the keys.. hrhrhr."
    Ko "Será tuya, junto con el collar y las llaves... jejeje."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1319
translate spanish scene4_ivy_0e8913b7:

    # Zt "It seems I have multiple options."
    Zt "Parece que tengo múltiples opciones."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1320
translate spanish scene4_ivy_f2c9f3f5:

    # Zt "1. I can make them hand the girl over, one way or another."
    Zt "1. Puedo hacer que entreguen a la chica de una manera u otra."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1321
translate spanish scene4_ivy_11077318:

    # Zt "The locals won't be happy about this."
    Zt "A los locales no les hará gracia esto."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1322
translate spanish scene4_ivy_f11d9200:

    # Zt "2. I can give them the statue of Bastet and buy the elf."
    Zt "2. Puedo darles la estatua de Bastet y comprar a la elfa."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1323
translate spanish scene4_ivy_ed0d8dbe:

    # Zt "The Queen will not reward me if I show up empty handed."
    Zt "La Reina no me recompensará si aparezco con las manos vacías."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1325
translate spanish scene4_ivy_dfec4672:

    # Zt "3. I can wash my hands of this and let them finish off the elf."
    Zt "3. Puedo lavarme las manos y dejar que terminen con la elfa."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1326
translate spanish scene4_ivy_b285e451:

    # Zt "But mutants are rare, and her particular kind even more so. I must admit I am curious."
    Zt "Pero los mutantes son raros, y su tipo en particular aún más. Debo admitir que tengo curiosidad."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1336
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_e64db6f4:

    # "You have known for a long time that the decayed are cannibals, but having it thrown in your face like this makes your blood boil."
    "Sabías desde hace mucho que los decayed son caníbales, pero que te lo arrojen a la cara así hace que tu sangre hierva."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1337
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_a51b6805:

    # Z "You disgust me. I have seen all kinds of sick shit but this goes too far."
    Z "Me das asco. He visto toda clase de mierda enfermiza, pero esto es demasiado."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1339
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_12bfca89:

    # Z "Hand the girl over, I am not making any deals today."
    Z "Entrega a la chica, no estoy haciendo tratos hoy."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1340
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_09c75e1d:

    # Ko "Whoa, what's gotten into you Master [persistent.player_name]?!"
    Ko "Vaya, ¿qué te pasa Amo [persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1341
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_9ea46411:

    # Ki "Yeah, what the fuck? This is [Ko]'s catch; it's his property!"
    Ki "Cierto, ¿qué coño? Esta es la captura de [Ko]; ¡es de su propiedad!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1342
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_8fca5028:

    # Ko "It belongs to me, and if I want to make a snack of it, I fucking will!"
    Ko "Me pertenece y, si quiero hacer un bocadillo con ello, ¡lo haré, joder!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1343
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_c95a8478:

    # Z "This is not a discussion."
    Z "Esto no se trata de un debate."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1344
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_2dabaefb:

    # Z "You can choose to give her to me, or I will make you."
    Z "Puedes elegir dármela, o me encargaré de hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1345
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_fa2446fd:

    # Ki "And then what?! Everyone will know you dishonored the agreement!!"
    Ki "¿Y después qué?! ¡Todos sabrán que deshonraste el acuerdo!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1347
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_3726e1e2:

    # Z "Oh you're probably right... let me think about that for a second..."
    Z "Oh, probablemente tengas razón... déjame pensarlo un segundo..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1351
translate spanish ivychoicemenu_7f6df47f:

    # Z "I'll take that risk."
    Z "Me arriesgaré."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1363
translate spanish cs6_77cc7753:

    # Ko "..!"
    Ko "¡..!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1364
translate spanish cs6_13f2e0c6:

    # Ki "What the fuck [persistent.player_name]?!"
    Ki "¡¿Qué cojones [persistent.player_name]?!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1367
translate spanish cs6_cb93037e:

    # Ki "You're going to regret thi-"
    Ki "Te vas a arrepentir de esto-"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1377
translate spanish cs9_36321dd2:

    # Ki "...hrrrgh!"
    Ki "¡...hrrrgh!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1381
translate spanish cs9_a4b4fe16:

    # Z "Fucking degenerates."
    Z "Malditos degenerados."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1384
translate spanish cs9_888a0726:

    # Z "Hey. Are you okay?"
    Z "Oye... ¿estás bien?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1387
translate spanish cs9_108ab3cd:

    # Elf "..."
    Elf "..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1388
translate spanish cs9_c79444a7:

    # Z "We don't have much time."
    Z "No tenemos mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1389
translate spanish cs9_6a0623ff:

    # Z "If they see us here, they will find out what happened."
    Z "Si nos ven aquí, se enterarán de lo que ha pasado."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1390
translate spanish cs9_abb7885f:

    # Z "There's a car outside. Get in it, and don't make a sound."
    Z "Hay un coche fuera. Entra en él y no hagas ruido."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1391
translate spanish cs9_c71e93b2:

    # Z "I will take the keys and catch up soon."
    Z "Cogeré las llaves y te alcanzaré pronto."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1392
translate spanish cs9_dc3872d6:

    # Z "The collar can't hurt you. I won't be far."
    Z "El collar no puede hacerte daño. No estaré lejos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1396
translate spanish cs9_152c2774:

    # "{i}You and the elf leave the ruins and she heads to the car..."
    "{i}Tú y la elfa salís de las ruinas y ella se dirige al coche..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1408
translate spanish cs9_6e4a1255:

    # Z "Let's make the deal. The girl for this artifact I found."
    Z "Hagamos el trato. La chica por este artefacto que encontré."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1412
translate spanish cs9_a5ee55fa:

    # Ki "Now that's a great reminder why the decayed like you [persistent.player_name]! Hrhrhr..."
    Ki "¡Eso sí que es un buen recordatorio de por qué los Decaídos te quieren tanto, [persistent.player_name]! Jejeje..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1413
translate spanish cs9_85812ae7:

    # Ko "Damn it, I was looking forward to a good meal..."
    Ko "¡Joder, estaba deseando una buena comida!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1415
translate spanish cs9_6ad4cdbd:

    # Ki "Don't be stupid, [Ko]. That artifact is worth many meals, to the right buyer..."
    Ki "No seas estúpido, [Ko]. Ese artefacto vale muchas comidas, para el comprador adecuado..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1416
translate spanish cs9_a1049c9a:

    # Ko "I'm still hungry though... hrhrhr."
    Ko "Pero sigo hambriento... hrhrhr."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1417
translate spanish cs9_4be7ea75:

    # Ko "Why don't you visit us again soon, [persistent.player_name]?"
    Ko "¿Por qué no vuelves a visitarnos pronto, [persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1418
translate spanish cs9_abad44d6:

    # Ko "We have known you for so long now, and you're a man of your word."
    Ko "Te conocemos desde hace mucho tiempo y eres un hombre de palabra."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1419
translate spanish cs9_fe3cc014:

    # Ko "Next time you come here we will show you around a little...as a sign of trust. Hrhrhr.."
    Ko "La próxima vez que vengas, te mostraremos un poco... como señal de confianza. Hrhrhr..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1420
translate spanish cs9_520744b7:

    # Ki "[persistent.player_name!c], take the keys, the girl will follow you as if her life depends on it... because it-"
    Ki "[persistent.player_name!c], coge las llaves, la chica te sigue como si su vida dependiera de ello... porque..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1421
translate spanish cs9_d6a0cb63:

    # Z "Yeah yeah because it does, very funny.. Now, I need to get going. I'll see you around..."
    Z "Sí, sí, porque sí lo hace, muy gracioso... Ahora, tengo que irme. Nos vemos..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1422
translate spanish cs9_02e53e4e:

    # Zt "...you ugly motherfuckers."
    Zt "... feos hijos de puta."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1430
translate spanish cs9_494a308c:

    # "You take the keys and lead the girl to your car. She'll wait inside."
    "Coges las llaves y llevas a la chica a tu coche. Ella esperará dentro."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1441
translate spanish cs9_21f24193:

    # Z "I don't care about the girl, I'll keep the artifact for myself."
    Z "No me importa la chica, me quedaré con el artefacto para mí."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1444
translate spanish cs9_a2170e5e:

    # Ko "As you wish, Master [persistent.player_name]."
    Ko "Como quieras, Amo [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1445
translate spanish cs9_4d3c8a93:

    # Ko "Not the reaction I expected, but well..."
    Ko "No es la reacción que esperaba, pero bueno..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1446
translate spanish cs9_c8b0a433:

    # Ki "Now to the good part... hrhrhr..."
    Ki "Ahora la parte buena... jejeje..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1447
translate spanish cs9_0ed1f9e0:

    # Ko "Yes, finally... I am starving."
    Ko "Sí, finalmente... estoy muerto de hambre."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1450
translate spanish cs9_108ab3cd_1:

    # Elf "..."
    Elf "..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1451
translate spanish cs9_b2f47604:

    # Ko "All I need to do... is push this button..."
    Ko "Todo lo que tengo que hacer... es pulsar este botón..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1452
translate spanish cs9_a40c6795:

    # Ko "...aaand.."
    Ko "... yyy ..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1463
translate spanish cs9_e819742f:

    # Ki "Haaaa!! What a mess!!"
    Ki "¡¡Aaaah!! ¡¡Qué lío!!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1464
translate spanish cs9_addd627c:

    # Ki "Look she's still twitching."
    Ki "Mira, todavía se está sacudiendo."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1467
translate spanish cs9_50721a9b:

    # Ko "Hrhrhr! A good catch!"
    Ko "¡Hrhrhr! ¡Una buena captura!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1474
translate spanish cs9_fa72a0e3:

    # Ki "I don't think I have had an Elven mutant before."
    Ki "No creo haber tenido nunca un mutante elfo antes."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1477
translate spanish cs9_1e4506ba:

    # Ko "You're a good partner, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ko "Eres un buen socio, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1478
translate spanish cs9_cb6fa672:

    # Ko "Why not visit us again sometime in the future..."
    Ko "¿Por qué no vuelves a visitarnos alguna vez en el futuro?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1479
translate spanish cs9_07c8c524:

    # Ko "[Ki] and me want to show you around a bit."
    Ko "[Ki] y yo queremos enseñarte un poco la zona."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1482
translate spanish cs9_730c291d:

    # Ko "Now if you excuse us, we have a meal to prepare, hrhrhr."
    Ko "Si nos disculpas, tenemos una comida que preparar, hrhrhr."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1486
translate spanish cs9_3fd92ae8:

    # "You take the collar and the keys and head back to your car, a bad taste lingering in your mouth, as you reflect on the repulsive nature of the Decayed."
    "Tomas el collar y las llaves y vuelves a tu coche, con un mal sabor de boca mientras reflexionas sobre la repulsiva naturaleza de los Decayed."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1493
translate spanish d1_drive_home_435ecd4d:

    # Z "There's nothing left for me to do here..."
    Z "No me queda nada por hacer aquí..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1495
translate spanish d1_drive_home_13617e35:

    # Z "Time to leave this god forsaken place and go home."
    Z "Es hora de abandonar este maldito lugar e ir a casa."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1504
translate spanish d1c_aff9a8e8:

    # "{i}Many hours later..."
    "{i}Muchas horas después..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1514
translate spanish d1c_215436bb:

    # Zt "Finally... coming home is the greatest reward."
    Zt "Finalmente... volver a casa es la mejor recompensa."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1515
translate spanish d1c_c973af4b:

    # Zt "Not many other people I know can afford to build a home of this quality, in a place of their choosing.."
    Zt "No muchas otras personas que conozco pueden permitirse construir un hogar de esta calidad, en el lugar de su elección."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1516
translate spanish d1c_03d50f80:

    # Zt "I have worked hard, exploring ruins, scouring many paths. I have built a solid network of contacts and leads, leading to more work and, ultimately, more resources."
    Zt "He trabajado duro, explorando ruinas, recorriendo muchos caminos. He construido una sólida red de contactos y pistas, llevando a más trabajo y, en última instancia, más recursos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1517
translate spanish d1c_91a52875:

    # Zt "It took many years, but finally I'm where I want to be."
    Zt "Tomó muchos años, pero finalmente estoy donde quiero estar."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1519
translate spanish d1c_2dd482f9:

    # Zt "It's good to be home."
    Zt "Es bueno estar en casa."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1522
translate spanish d1c_a25916bc:

    # Z "I'm back! Anyone home?"
    Z "¡He vuelto! ¿Hay alguien en casa?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1523
translate spanish d1c_fe5ae553:

    # C "Yes, I'll be right there."
    C "Sí, ya voy."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1531
translate spanish d1c_eb3dc944:

    # W "Please come in, love."
    W "Por favor, entra, amor."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1534
translate spanish d1c_d0c0cbb9:

    # "You step through the door in the gate..."
    "Pasas por la puerta en la verja..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1537
translate spanish d1c_10bffd68:

    # "That would be my wife. Beautiful, loyal, and the woman who truly runs this household."
    "Esa sería mi mujer. Hermosa, leal y la mujer que realmente maneja esta casa."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1538
translate spanish d1c_b1f86579:

    # "We have been together for a couple of decades now.."
    "Hemos estado juntos un par de décadas ya..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1542
translate spanish d1c_1453d895:

    # W "It's been a few days too long."
    W "Han sido unos días demasiado largos."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1545
translate spanish d1c_ac0752c6:

    # Z "All the more exciting to come back to you."
    Z "Es aún más emocionante volver a ti."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1548
translate spanish d1c_3564a740:

    # W "We're always happy to have you back."
    W "Siempre nos alegra tenerte de vuelta."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1551
translate spanish d1c_ad092978:

    # W "And you don't seem to be hurt this time. You know how to make my day."
    W "Y no parece que estés herido esta vez. Sabes cómo alegrarme el día."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1554
translate spanish d1c_da053e20:

    # Z "What about you, is everything alright?"
    Z "¿Y tú, todo bien?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1559
translate spanish d1c_961d17d7:

    # Zt "I am their [persistent.dad]. They usually call me dad though."
    Zt "Soy su [persistent.dad]. Aunque normalmente me llaman papá."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1575
translate spanish d1c_4efa5b7c:

    # A "Um... hey... guys?"
    A "Um... ey... ¿chicos?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1576
translate spanish d1c_c2c9cc07:

    # W "..."
    W "..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1579
translate spanish d1c_f27a717c:

    # "Before [W] was able to respond, another member of your house stepped outside, dressed in an outfit matching a dancer..."
    "Antes de que [W] pudiera responder, otro miembro de tu casa salió afuera, vestido con un atuendo de bailarina..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1582
translate spanish d1c_8a715439:

    # A "Sorry... I am late again..."
    A "Lo siento... llego tarde otra vez..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1585
translate spanish d1c_0c02ecbf:

    # W "{i}*sigh*{/i} Well, husband... there you have your answer."
    W "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Bueno, marido... ahí tienes tu respuesta."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1586
translate spanish d1c_74fb35a9:

    # "Playful pigtails, and prone to causing distress to my wife."
    "Coletas juguetonas, y propensa a causar angustia a mi mujer."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1591
translate spanish d1c_0005d6e5:

    # W "Already an adult, and you still find it entertaining to take your [persistent.mom]'s clothes..."
    W "Ya es adulta, y aún le parece entretenido ponerse la ropa de su [persistent.mom]..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1594
translate spanish d1c_c9a715a5:

    # A "But [persistent.dad] likes it, right? I look just like one of those dancers in the city now."
    A "Pero a [persistent.dad] le gusta, ¿verdad? Ahora parezco una de esas bailarinas de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1595
translate spanish d1c_f9e9ea77:

    # A "You know...like the ones you brought home a couple of times."
    A "Sabes... como las que trajiste a casa un par de veces."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1598
translate spanish d1c_47f5f961:

    # A "I know it's [persistent.mom]'s dress..."
    A "Sé que es el vestido de [persistent.mom]..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1599
translate spanish d1c_fb55afbd:

    # A "But I think it fits me better."
    A "Pero creo que a mí me queda mejor."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1607
translate spanish d1c_menu_c1919a54:

    # Z "[A]... listen..."
    Z "[A]... escucha..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1608
translate spanish d1c_menu_0a614ee4:

    # Z "You know you can't do that."
    Z "Sabes que no puedes hacer eso."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1609
translate spanish d1c_menu_8ff9553d:

    # Z "If the guards or other people from the city saw you..."
    Z "Si los guardias u otras personas de la ciudad te vieran..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1612
translate spanish d1c_menu_be4268db:

    # Z "It's not safe enough."
    Z "No es lo suficientemente seguro."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1613
translate spanish d1c_menu_3d099ebc:

    # Z "That's why you will only wear it when I tell you to, alright?"
    Z "Por eso sólo te lo pondrás cuando yo te lo diga, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1616
translate spanish d1c_menu_eaf29c03:

    # A "Fine, [persistent.dad]."
    A "Bien, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1620
translate spanish d1c_menu_dcec0717:

    # Z "Also... there is a girl in the car. She is unconscious."
    Z "Además... hay una chica en el coche. Está inconsciente."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1623
translate spanish d1c_menu_a6b28a28:

    # Z "It doesn't look like she is dangerous, but we don't know what her intentions are yet."
    Z "No parece peligrosa, pero no sabemos cuáles son sus intenciones."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1624
translate spanish d1c_menu_5f2b7657:

    # Z "I need you to escort her into the basement. She's starving. Make sure to bring her a good meal, and make it a large portion too."
    Z "Necesito que la lleves al sótano. Está hambrienta. Asegúrate de llevarle una buena comida, y que sea una porción grande también."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1627
translate spanish d1c_menu_5f775b5e:

    # A "Okay! I'm on it!"
    A "¡Vale! ¡Enseguida!"

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1630
translate spanish d1c_menu_39fe6fc9:

    # W "Na-ah, I don't think so. Allow me to see about it instead."
    W "No, no lo creo. Permíteme encargarme de esto en su lugar."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1631
translate spanish d1c_menu_07270ac6:

    # W "You may see your other [persistent.da], if you wish."
    W "Puedes ver a tu otra [persistent.da], si quieres."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1634
translate spanish d1c_menu_67682501:

    # W "In the meantime, [A] and I will have a word with each other."
    W "Mientras tanto, [A] y yo tendremos una charla."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1637
translate spanish d1c_menu_bc57f8af:

    # W "And about her habit of stealing my dresses..."
    W "Y sobre su costumbre de robarme mis vestidos..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1647
translate spanish d1c_menu_52ed762b:

    # Zt "Holy Merneith..."
    Zt "Santa Merneith..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1650
translate spanish d1c_menu_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1654
translate spanish d1c_menu_aae4963b:

    # Z "Enough of this."
    Z "Ya está bien de esto."

# game/scripts/day1.rpy:1657
